Ruiz-Rodriguez v. ARAMARK Cleanroom Services, LLC, et al
                



Plaintiff:
Marjorie Joan Ruiz-Rodriguez and Conjugal Partnership Negron-Ruiz


Defendant:
ARAMARK Cleanroom Services, LLC, ARAMARK Cleanroom Services (Puerto Rico), Inc., John Doe, Jane Doe and ABC Insurance Company


Case Number:
3:2010cv01135


Filed:
February 18, 2010


Court:
Puerto Rico District Court


Office:
San Juan Office


County:
Bayamon


Presiding Judge:
Jose A Fuste


Nature of Suit:
Tort Product Liability


Cause of Action:
28:1441 Notice of Removal


Jury Demanded By:
None



