Aramark Cleanroom Services, LLC Overview
  Aramark Cleanroom Services, LLC filed as a Foreign Limited Liability Company (LLC) in the State of Texas on Friday, June 8, 2007 and is approximately ten years old, according to public records filed with Texas Secretary of State. A corporate filing is called a foreign filing when an existing corporate entity files in a state other than the state they originally filed in. This does not necessarily mean that they are from outside the United States.   




